# Goal Description

Build an audiophile e-commerce landing page with a minimalist, industrial "dark mode" aesthetic. We will set up the global layout (Navbar, Footer) and the main Landing Page content (Hero, Featured Categories, Trending Products).

## User Review Required

None for the initial setup.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Setup
- Initialize Next.js project with App Router and Tailwind CSS
- Install `framer-motion`, `zustand`, `lucide-react`
- Setup custom Tailwind theme with deep carbon blacks (`#0F0F0F`) and neon orange (`#FF4500`) accents.

### Global Layout
- `src/components/layout/Navbar.tsx`: Responsive top navigation with logo, links, and cart icon.
- `src/components/layout/Footer.tsx`: Minimalist footer.
- `src/app/layout.tsx`: Root layout with dark mode styles and noise texture base.

### Landing Page Content
- `src/app/page.tsx`: Main page assembling the sections.
- `src/components/customer/Hero.tsx`: High-impact hero section with staggered entrance.
- `src/components/customer/FeaturedCategories.tsx`: Asymmetric grid highlighting Audio gear categories.
- `src/components/customer/TrendingProducts.tsx`: Carousel/grid of mock products.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Type checking (`tsc --noEmit`).
- Starting dev server and rendering the page natively.

### Manual Verification
- Review the aesthetic and responsive layout visually.
